		<ul> (unordered/bullet list) or the <ol> (ordered/numbered list) tag, followed by <li> tags (list items)
		<ul>
             <li>Coffee</li>
             <li>Tea</li>
             <li>Milk</li>
         </ul>
		 
		 <bdo dir="rtl">This text will be written from right to left</bdo>
				
				
